languages.text: "Впрочем, пока вы сохраняете инкогнито, вам будет трудно воспользоваться этой привилегией. Помните об этом, если пожелаете пообщаться с менее осведомленными обитателями станции — для них вы являетесь обычн{mf|ым|ой} гост{mf|ем|ьей} Футфола".

"However, as long as you remain incognito, it will be difficult for you to use this privilege. Keep this in mind if you wish to communicate with the less knowledgeable inhabitants of the station — for them you are an ordinary visitor to Footfall."

languages.text: 「しかし身分を明かさない限り、この特権を利用することは難しい。ステーションのあまり知識のない住民とコミュニケーションを取るなら、このことを念頭に置いてほしい。彼らにとって、君はフットフォールへ来たただのお客だ」
languages.original_text: "However, as long as you remain incognito, it will be difficult for you to use this privilege. Keep this in mind if you wish to communicate with the less knowledgeable inhabitants of the station — for them you are an ordinary visitor to Footfall."

languages.text: “不过，若是您始终隐姓埋名，您就很难行使这样的特权。如果您打算和落脚港那些不太懂行的人交流，请务必记住这一点：对他们来说，您只是一个普通的过客罢了。”

languages.text: «No obstante, mientras permanezca de incógnito, le resultará difícil hacer uso de este privilegio. Téngalo en cuenta si pretende entablar conversación con los habitantes menos avezados de la estación; para ellos, usted es {mf|un|una} visitante más de Paso».
languages.original_text: "However, as long as you remain incognito, it will be difficult for you to use this privilege. Keep this in mind if you wish to communicate with the less knowledgeable inhabitants of the station — for them you are an ordinary visitor to Footfall."

languages.text: « Cependant, tant que vous resterez ici incognito, vous aurez le plus grand mal à profiter de ce privilège. Si vous souhaitez communiquer avec les habitants les moins éclairés de la station, gardez bien à l'esprit que pour eux, vous n'êtes qu'{mf|un visiteur|une visiteuse} comme les autres à Castel. »

languages.text: "Doch solange Ihr inkognito bleibt, wird es schwierig sein, dieses Privileg zu nutzen. Denkt daran, wenn Ihr mit den weniger gebildeten Einwohnern dieser Station sprecht – für sie seid Ihr {mf|ein gewöhnlicher Besucher|eine gewöhnliche Besucherin} von Footfall."

languages.text: "Lakin kimliğinizi saklı tuttuğunuz müddetçe bu ayrıcalığı kullanmanız zor olacaktır. İstasyonun eğitimi noksan sakinleriyle iletişim kurmak istiyorsanız aklınızda bulunsun, onlar için Binliman'da sıradan bir ziyaretçisiniz."
languages.original_text: "However, as long as you remain incognito, it will be difficult for you to use this privilege. Keep this in mind if you wish to communicate with the less knowledgeable inhabitants of the station — for them you are an ordinary visitor to Footfall."

traits.locale_text: "Lakin gizli kaldığınız sürece bu ayrıcalığı kullanmanız zor olacaktır. İstasyonun muttali olmayan sakinleriyle iletişim kurmak istiyorsanız aklınızda bulunsun, onlar için Binliman'da sıradan bir ziyaretçisiniz."
